{"tid":1506573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[踩死曱甴] 有市民跪地要求不要開槍被踢　警方稱動作屬自然反應","createTime":"2019-08-26T00:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T00:34:21.000Z","uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1bc0d750e6c3a376976e25a58ff5bbc01ae452","tid":1506573,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:18:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476781-20190826.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476781-20190826.htm&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=c1ed346f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476781-20190826.htm&h=e7c50052\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476781-20190826.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚在荃灣進行驅散行動期間，有市民跪地要求不要開槍，有警員踢向他。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科高級警司余鎧均表示，當時警務人員生命受到嚴重威脅，而她留意到事發時有人在警方擎槍後「在地下有一個動作」，形容警方當時的動作屬「自然反應」。<br />\n<br />\n余鎧均又說，當時很難分清楚該名人士是示威者抑或暴徒，又說有時亦不知道著上背心的人，是否真正記者，強調行動目的是要保障市民及警員自身安全。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有多少人被捕，以及是否有一名12歲少年被捕，她指行動仍在進行，稍後交代被捕人數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/698899/org/2c5057fe33d842e59594766ba8e07744.jpg/GzjKpN4Prz8wbkhJlayQMW4lR-fRmn-WRYVArUWFQK0?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F698899%2Forg%2F2c5057fe33d842e59594766ba8e07744.jpg%2FGzjKpN4Prz8wbkhJlayQMW4lR-fRmn-WRYVArUWFQK0%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=d0fb68df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfa928704d028ab2b765d07074e9c9ea79e1ff46","tid":1506573,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:19:42.000Z","msg":"ON9"},{"pid":"8adf6539fd3af40d9708fdb564b1465912f61e3c","tid":1506573,"uid":6840,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:20:19.000Z","msg":"打狗都係自然反應"},{"pid":"caa6e7e82c77c402427871a629268393f4eae38e","tid":1506573,"uid":40287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"